data.description: Check out this gorgeous 4 level home with amazing views located in the desirable Highland Estates area. This 4 bedroom, 3 bath home offers stylish LVP flooring, granite counter-tops, stainless appliances and vaulted ceilings. The private dining room features floor to ceiling glass. Enjoy a cozy family room just off the kitchen and park your toys in the three-car garage. Entertain your guests in an amazing backyard complete with deck, waterfall, and hot-tub. Sellers offering $2500 credit for interior paint or closing cost assistance.
